38void ABattleObject::Move()
39{
40 if (IsPlayer)
41 {
42 if (Player->PlayerFlags & PLF_IsThrowLock)
43 return;
44 Player->SetHitValuesOverTime();
45 }
46 else if (PositionLinkObj)
47 {
48 PrevPosX = PositionLinkObj->PrevPosX;
49 PrevPosY = PositionLinkObj->PrevPosY;
50 PosX = PositionLinkObj->PosX;
51 PosY = PositionLinkObj->PosY;
52 return;
53 }
54
55 // Set previous pos values
56 PrevPosX = PosX;
57 PrevPosY = PosY;
58 CalculateHoming();
59
60 if (BlendOffset && BlendCelName != FGameplayTag::EmptyTag && MaxCelTime)
61 {
62 const int32 TmpOffsetX = (NextOffsetX - PrevOffsetX) * (MaxCelTime - TimeUntilNextCel) / MaxCelTime;
63 const int32 TmpOffsetY = (NextOffsetY - PrevOffsetY) * (MaxCelTime - TimeUntilNextCel) / MaxCelTime;
64
65 AddPosXWithDir(TmpOffsetX);
66 PosY += TmpOffsetY;
67 }
68
69 SpeedX = SpeedX * SpeedXRatePerFrame / 100;
70 SpeedY = SpeedY * SpeedYRatePerFrame / 100;
71 SpeedZ = SpeedZ * SpeedZRatePerFrame / 100;
72 SpeedX = SpeedX * SpeedXRate / 100;
73 SpeedY = SpeedY * SpeedYRate / 100;
74 SpeedZ = SpeedZ * SpeedZRate / 100;
75
76 SpeedXRate = SpeedYRate = SpeedZRate = 100;
77
78 if (MiscFlags & MISC_InertiaEnable) //only use inertia if enabled
79 {
80 if (PosY <= GroundHeight && MiscFlags & MISC_FloorCollisionActive) //only decrease inertia if grounded
81 {
82 Inertia = Inertia - Inertia / 10;
83 }
84 if (Inertia > -875 && Inertia < 875) //if inertia small enough, set to zero
85 {
86 Inertia = 0;
87 }
88 AddPosXWithDir(Inertia);
89 }
90
91 if (IsPlayer)
92 {
93 int32 ModifiedPushback;
94 if (PosY > GroundHeight)
95 ModifiedPushback = Player->Pushback * 84;
96 else if (Player->Stance == ACT_Crouching)
97 ModifiedPushback = Player->Pushback * 86;
98 else
99 ModifiedPushback = Player->Pushback * 88;
100
101 Player->Pushback = ModifiedPushback / 100;
102
103 if (PosY <= GroundHeight || !(Player->PlayerFlags & PLF_IsStunned))
104 AddPosXWithDir(Player->Pushback);
105 }
106
107 AddPosXWithDir(SpeedX); //apply speed
108
109 if (IsPlayer && Player != nullptr)
110 {
111 if (Player->AirDashTimer == 0 || (SpeedY > 0 && ActionTime < 5)) // only set y speed if not airdashing/airdash startup not done
112 {
113 PosY += SpeedY;
114 if (PosY > GroundHeight || !(MiscFlags & MISC_FloorCollisionActive))
115 SpeedY -= Gravity;
116 }
117 else
118 {
119 SpeedY = 0;
120 }
121 }
122 else
123 {
124 PosY += SpeedY;
125 if (PosY > GroundHeight || !(MiscFlags & MISC_FloorCollisionActive))
126 SpeedY -= Gravity;
127 }
128
129 if (PosY < GroundHeight && MiscFlags & MISC_FloorCollisionActive) //if on ground, force y values to zero
130 {
131 PosY = GroundHeight;
132 }
133
134 PosZ += SpeedZ;
135}

137void ABattleObject::CalculateHoming()
138{
139 if (HomingParams.Target != OBJ_Null)
140 {
141 ABattleObject* Target = GetBattleObject(HomingParams.Target);
142
143 if (Target != nullptr)
144 {
145 int32 TargetPosX = 0;
146 int32 TargetPosY = 0;
147
148 Target->PosTypeToPosition(HomingParams.Pos, &TargetPosX, &TargetPosY);
149
150 const bool TargetFacingRight = Target->Direction == DIR_Right;
151 int32 HomingOffsetX = -HomingParams.OffsetX;
152 if (!TargetFacingRight)
153 HomingOffsetX = HomingParams.OffsetX;
154
155 if (HomingParams.Type == HOMING_DistanceAccel)
156 {
157 int32 TmpPosY = TargetPosY + HomingParams.OffsetY - PosY;
158 int32 TmpPosX = TargetPosX + HomingOffsetX - PosX;
159 SpeedXRatePerFrame = HomingParams.ParamB;
160 SpeedYRatePerFrame = HomingParams.ParamB;
161 AddSpeedXRaw(HomingParams.ParamA * TmpPosX / 100);
162 SpeedY += HomingParams.ParamA * TmpPosY / 100;
163 }
164 else if (HomingParams.Type == HOMING_FixAccel)
165 {
166 int32 TmpPosY = TargetPosY + HomingParams.OffsetY - PosY;
167 int32 TmpPosX = TargetPosX + HomingOffsetX - PosX;
168 int32 Angle = UNightSkyBlueprintFunctionLibrary::Vec2Angle_x1000(TmpPosX, TmpPosY) / 100;
169 SpeedXRate = HomingParams.ParamB;
170 SpeedYRate = HomingParams.ParamB;
171 int32 CosParamA = HomingParams.ParamA * UNightSkyBlueprintFunctionLibrary::Cos_x1000(Angle) / 1000;
172 int32 SinParamA = HomingParams.ParamA * UNightSkyBlueprintFunctionLibrary::Sin_x1000(Angle) / 1000;
173 AddSpeedXRaw(CosParamA);
174 SpeedY += SinParamA;
175 }
176 else if (HomingParams.Type == HOMING_ToSpeed)
177 {
178 int32 TmpPosY = TargetPosY + HomingParams.OffsetY - PosY;
179 int32 TmpPosX = TargetPosX + HomingOffsetX - PosX;
180 int32 Angle = UNightSkyBlueprintFunctionLibrary::Vec2Angle_x1000(TmpPosX, TmpPosY) / 100;
181 int32 CosParamA = (Direction == DIR_Right ? HomingParams.ParamA : -HomingParams.ParamA) * UNightSkyBlueprintFunctionLibrary::Cos_x1000(Angle) / 1000;
182 int32 SinParamA = HomingParams.ParamA * UNightSkyBlueprintFunctionLibrary::Sin_x1000(Angle) / 1000;
183 int32 TmpParamB = Direction == DIR_Right ? HomingParams.ParamB : -HomingParams.ParamB;
184 int32 TmpSpeedX = Direction == DIR_Right ? SpeedX : -SpeedX;
185 if (TmpParamB <= 0)
186 {
187 if (TmpParamB >= 0)
188 {
189 CosParamA = TmpSpeedX;
190 }
191 else if (TmpSpeedX < CosParamA && -TmpSpeedX > CosParamA)
192 {
193 CosParamA = TmpParamB + TmpSpeedX;
194 }
195 while (TmpSpeedX - CosParamA <= TmpParamB || -TmpSpeedX + CosParamA >= TmpParamB)
196 {
197 SetSpeedXRaw(-CosParamA);
198 if (HomingParams.ParamB <= 0)
199 {
200 if (HomingParams.ParamB >= 0)
201 {
202 return;
203 }
204 if (SpeedY < SinParamA)
205 {
206 SinParamA = SpeedY + HomingParams.ParamB;
207 }
208 SpeedY = SinParamA;
209 return;
210 }
211 if (SpeedY < SinParamA)
212 {
213 if (SinParamA - SpeedY > HomingParams.ParamB)
214 {
215 SinParamA = SpeedY + HomingParams.ParamB;
216 }
217 }
218 if (SpeedY - SinParamA <= HomingParams.ParamB)
219 {
220 SpeedY = SinParamA;
221 return;
222 }
223 SinParamA = SpeedY - HomingParams.ParamB;
224 SpeedY = SinParamA;
225 return;
226 }
227 }
228 else
229 {
230 if (TmpSpeedX < CosParamA)
231 {
232 if (CosParamA - TmpSpeedX > TmpParamB)
233 {
234 CosParamA = TmpParamB + TmpSpeedX;
235 }
236 while (TmpSpeedX - CosParamA <= TmpParamB || -TmpSpeedX + CosParamA >= TmpParamB)
237 {
238 SetSpeedXRaw(CosParamA);
239 if (HomingParams.ParamB <= 0)
240 {
241 if (HomingParams.ParamB >= 0)
242 {
243 SinParamA = SpeedY;
244 }
245 if (SpeedY < SinParamA)
246 {
247 SinParamA = SpeedY + HomingParams.ParamB;
248 }
249 SpeedY = SinParamA;
250 return;
251 }
252 if (SpeedY < SinParamA)
253 {
254 if (SinParamA - SpeedY > HomingParams.ParamB)
255 {
256 SinParamA = SpeedY + HomingParams.ParamB;
257 }
258 }
259 if (SpeedY - SinParamA <= HomingParams.ParamB)
260 {
261 SpeedY = SinParamA;
262 return;
263 }
264 SinParamA = SpeedY - HomingParams.ParamB;
265 SpeedY = SinParamA;
266 return;
267 }
268 }
269 if (TmpSpeedX - CosParamA <= TmpParamB)
270 {
271 while (TmpSpeedX - CosParamA <= TmpParamB || -TmpSpeedX + CosParamA >= TmpParamB)
272 {
273 SetSpeedXRaw(CosParamA);
274 if (HomingParams.ParamB <= 0)
275 {
276 if (HomingParams.ParamB >= 0)
277 {
278 SinParamA = SpeedY;
279 }
280 if (SpeedY < SinParamA)
281 {
282 SinParamA = SpeedY + HomingParams.ParamB;
283 }
284 SpeedY = SinParamA;
285 return;
286 }
287 if (SpeedY < SinParamA)
288 {
289 if (SinParamA - SpeedY > HomingParams.ParamB)
290 {
291 SinParamA = SpeedY + HomingParams.ParamB;
292 }
293 }
294 if (SpeedY - SinParamA <= HomingParams.ParamB)
295 {
296 SpeedY = SinParamA;
297 return;
298 }
299 SinParamA = SpeedY - HomingParams.ParamB;
300 SpeedY = SinParamA;
301 return;
302 }
303 }
304 }
305 while (TmpSpeedX - CosParamA <= TmpParamB || -TmpSpeedX + CosParamA >= TmpParamB)
306 {
307 SetSpeedXRaw(CosParamA);
308 if (HomingParams.ParamB <= 0)
309 {
310 if (HomingParams.ParamB >= 0)
311 {
312 SinParamA = SpeedY;
313 }
314 if (SpeedY < SinParamA)
315 {
316 SinParamA = SpeedY + HomingParams.ParamB;
317 }
318 SpeedY = SinParamA;
319 return;
320 }
321 if (SpeedY < SinParamA)
322 {
323 if (SinParamA - SpeedY > HomingParams.ParamB)
324 {
325 SinParamA = SpeedY + HomingParams.ParamB;
326 }
327 }
328 if (SpeedY - SinParamA <= HomingParams.ParamB)
329 {
330 SpeedY = SinParamA;
331 return;
332 }
333 SinParamA = SpeedY - HomingParams.ParamB;
334 SpeedY = SinParamA;
335 return;
336 }
337 }
338 }
339 }

342bool ABattleObject::SuperArmorSuccess(const ABattleObject* Attacker) const
343{
344 if (SuperArmorData.Type == ARM_None) return false;
345 if (SuperArmorData.ArmorHits == 0) return false;
346
347 if (SuperArmorData.bArmorMid && Attacker->HitCommon.BlockType == BLK_Mid) return true;
348 if (SuperArmorData.bArmorOverhead && Attacker->HitCommon.BlockType == BLK_High) return true;
349 if (SuperArmorData.bArmorLow && Attacker->HitCommon.BlockType == BLK_Low) return true;
350 if (SuperArmorData.bArmorStrike && Attacker->AttackFlags & ATK_HitActive && !(Attacker->AttackFlags &
351 ATK_AttackProjectileAttribute)) return true;
352 if (SuperArmorData.bArmorThrow && Attacker->IsPlayer && Attacker->Player->PlayerFlags & PLF_ThrowActive) return true;
353 if (SuperArmorData.bArmorHead && Attacker->AttackFlags & ATK_HitActive && Attacker->AttackFlags &
354 ATK_AttackHeadAttribute) return true;
355 if (SuperArmorData.bArmorProjectile && Attacker->AttackFlags & ATK_HitActive && Attacker->AttackFlags &
356 ATK_AttackProjectileAttribute) return true;
357
358 return false;
359}

372void ABattleObject::CalculatePushbox()
373{
374 L = PosX - (PushWidth + PushWidthExtend) / 2;
375 R = PosX + (PushWidth + PushWidthExtend) / 2;
376 T = PosY + PushHeight;
377 B = PosY - PushHeightLow;
378}

380void ABattleObject::HandlePushCollision(ABattleObject* OtherObj)
381{
382 if (MiscFlags & MISC_PushCollisionActive && OtherObj->MiscFlags & MISC_PushCollisionActive)
383 {
384 if (Hitstop <= 0 && ((!OtherObj->IsPlayer || OtherObj->Player->PlayerFlags & PLF_IsThrowLock) == 0 || (!IsPlayer || Player->PlayerFlags & PLF_IsThrowLock) == 0))
385 {
386 if (T >= OtherObj->B && B <= OtherObj->T && R >= OtherObj->L && L <= OtherObj->R)
387 {
388 bool IsPushLeft;
389 int32 CollisionDepth;
390 if (PrevPosX == OtherObj->PrevPosX)
391 {
392 if (PosX == OtherObj->PosX)
393 {
394 if (IsPlayer == OtherObj->IsPlayer)
395 {
396 if (Player->WallTouchTimer == OtherObj->Player->WallTouchTimer)
397 {
398 IsPushLeft = Player->PlayerIndex > 0;
399 }
400 else
401 {
402 IsPushLeft = Player->WallTouchTimer > OtherObj->Player->WallTouchTimer;
403 if (PosX > 0)
404 {
405 IsPushLeft = Player->WallTouchTimer <= OtherObj->Player->WallTouchTimer;
406 }
407 }
408 }
409 else
410 {
411 IsPushLeft = IsPlayer > OtherObj->IsPlayer;
412 }
413 }
414 else
415 {
416 IsPushLeft = PosX < OtherObj->PosX;
417 }
418 }
419 else
420 {
421 IsPushLeft = PrevPosX < OtherObj->PrevPosX;
422 }
423 if (IsPushLeft)
424 {
425 CollisionDepth = OtherObj->L - R;
426 }
427 else
428 {
429 CollisionDepth = OtherObj->R - L;
430 }
431
432 if (OtherObj->PosX <= -(GameState->BattleState.StageBounds + GameState->BattleState.ScreenBounds)
433 || OtherObj->PosX >= GameState->BattleState.StageBounds + GameState->BattleState.ScreenBounds)
434 {
435 PosX += CollisionDepth;
436 }
437 else
438 {
439 OtherObj->PosX -= CollisionDepth / 2;
440 PosX += CollisionDepth / 2;
441 }
442
443 CalculatePushbox();
444 OtherObj->CalculatePushbox();
445 }
446 }
447 }
448}

450void ABattleObject::HandleHitCollision(ABattleObject* AttackedObj)
451{
452 if (AttackFlags & ATK_IsAttacking && AttackFlags & ATK_HitActive && AttackedObj->ObjectsToIgnoreHitsFrom.Find(this) == INDEX_NONE)
453 {
454 // refactor this mess into a function
455 if (AttackedObj->IsPlayer && AttackedObj->Player->InvulnFlags & INV_StrikeInvulnerable && !AttackedObj->Player->
456 StrikeInvulnerableTimer && AttackedObj != Player && (!(AttackFlags & ATK_AttackHeadAttribute &&
457 AttackedObj->Player->InvulnFlags & INV_HeadInvulnerable) && !(AttackFlags & ATK_AttackProjectileAttribute
458 && AttackedObj->Player->InvulnFlags & INV_ProjectileInvulnerable))) return;
459
460 auto AttackedPlayer = Cast<APlayerObject>(AttackedObj);
461 if (!AttackedPlayer) return;
462 for (int i = 0; i < CollisionArraySize; i++)
463 {
464 if (Boxes[i].Type == BOX_Hit)
465 {
466 for (int j = 0; j < CollisionArraySize; j++)
467 {
468 if (AttackedPlayer->Boxes[j].Type == BOX_Hurt)
469 {
470 FCollisionBox Hitbox = Boxes[i];
471
472 FCollisionBox Hurtbox = AttackedPlayer->Boxes[j];
473
474 if (Direction == DIR_Right)
475 {
476 Hitbox.PosX += PosX;
477 }
478 else
479 {
480 Hitbox.PosX = -Hitbox.PosX + PosX;
481 }
482 Hitbox.PosY += PosY;
483 if (AttackedPlayer->Direction == DIR_Right)
484 {
485 Hurtbox.PosX += AttackedPlayer->PosX;
486 }
487 else
488 {
489 Hurtbox.PosX = -Hurtbox.PosX + AttackedPlayer->PosX;
490 }
491 Hurtbox.PosY += AttackedPlayer->PosY;
492
493 if (Hitbox.PosY + Hitbox.SizeY / 2 >= Hurtbox.PosY - Hurtbox.SizeY / 2
494 && Hitbox.PosY - Hitbox.SizeY / 2 <= Hurtbox.PosY + Hurtbox.SizeY / 2
495 && Hitbox.PosX + Hitbox.SizeX / 2 >= Hurtbox.PosX - Hurtbox.SizeX / 2
496 && Hitbox.PosX - Hitbox.SizeX / 2 <= Hurtbox.PosX + Hurtbox.SizeX / 2)
497 {
498 AttackedPlayer->AttackOwner = this;
499 AttackedPlayer->ObjectsToIgnoreHitsFrom.AddUnique(this);
500 AttackedPlayer->StunTime = 2147483647;
501 AttackedPlayer->FaceOpponent();
502 AttackedPlayer->HaltMomentum();
503 AttackedPlayer->PlayerFlags |= PLF_IsStunned;
504 AttackFlags |= ATK_HasHit;
505 AttackTarget = AttackedPlayer;
506
507 int CollisionDepthX;
508 if (Hitbox.PosX < AttackedPlayer->PosX)
509 {
510 CollisionDepthX = AttackedPlayer->PosX - (Hitbox.PosX + Hitbox.SizeX / 2);
511 HitPosX = Hitbox.PosX + CollisionDepthX / 2;
512 }
513 else
514 {
515 CollisionDepthX = Hitbox.PosX - Hitbox.SizeX / 2 - AttackedPlayer->PosX;
516 HitPosX = Hitbox.PosX - CollisionDepthX / 2;
517 }
518 int CollisionDepthY;
519 int32 CenterPosY = AttackedPlayer->GetPosYCenter();
520 if (Hitbox.PosY < CenterPosY)
521 {
522 CollisionDepthY = CenterPosY - (Hitbox.PosY + Hitbox.SizeY / 2);
523 HitPosY = Hitbox.PosY + CollisionDepthY / 2;
524 }
525 else
526 {
527 CollisionDepthY = Hitbox.PosY - Hitbox.SizeY / 2 - CenterPosY;
528 HitPosY = Hitbox.PosY - CollisionDepthY / 2;
529 }
530
531 TriggerEvent(EVT_HitOrBlock);
532 if (AttackedPlayer->IsMainPlayer())
533 {
534 TriggerEvent(EVT_HitOrBlockMainPlayer);
535 }
536
537 if (AttackedPlayer->IsCorrectBlock(HitCommon.BlockType)) //check blocking
538 {
539 CreateCommonParticle(Particle_Guard, POS_Enemy,
540 FVector(0, 100, 0),
541 FRotator(HitCommon.HitAngle, 0, 0));
542 TriggerEvent(EVT_Block);
543 if (AttackedPlayer->IsMainPlayer())
544 {
545 TriggerEvent(EVT_BlockMainPlayer);
546 }
547
548 const int32 ChipDamage = NormalHit.Damage * HitCommon.ChipDamagePercent / 100;
549 AttackedPlayer->CurrentHealth -= ChipDamage;
550
551 const FHitData Data = InitHitDataByAttackLevel(false);
552 AttackedPlayer->ReceivedHitCommon = HitCommon;
553 AttackedPlayer->ReceivedHit = Data;
554
555 if (AttackedPlayer->CurrentHealth <= 0)
556 {
557 EHitAction HACT;
558
559 if (AttackedPlayer->PosY == AttackedPlayer->GroundHeight && !(AttackedPlayer->PlayerFlags & PLF_IsKnockedDown))
560 HACT = NormalHit.GroundHitAction;
561 else
562 HACT = NormalHit.AirHitAction;
563
564 AttackedPlayer->HandleHitAction(HACT);
565 }
566 else
567 {
568 AttackedPlayer->HandleBlockAction();
569 AttackedPlayer->AirDashTimer = 0;
570 if (AttackedPlayer->PlayerFlags & PLF_TouchingWall)
571 {
572 Pushback = AttackedPlayer->Pushback;
573 AttackedPlayer->Pushback = 0;
574 }
575 }
576 AttackedPlayer->AddMeter(NormalHit.Damage * AttackedPlayer->MeterPercentOnReceiveHitGuard / 100);
577 Player->AddMeter(NormalHit.Damage * Player->MeterPercentOnHitGuard / 100);
578 }
579 else if (AttackedPlayer->SuperArmorSuccess(this))
580 {
581 TriggerEvent(EVT_Hit);
582 if (AttackedPlayer->IsMainPlayer())
583 {
584 TriggerEvent(EVT_HitMainPlayer);
585 }
586
587 if (AttackedPlayer->SuperArmorData.ArmorHits > 0) AttackedPlayer->SuperArmorData.ArmorHits--;
588 switch (AttackedPlayer->SuperArmorData.Type)
589 {
590 case ARM_Guard:
591 {
592 if (AttackedPlayer->SuperArmorData.bArmorTakeChipDamage)
593 {
594 const int32 ChipDamage = NormalHit.Damage * HitCommon.ChipDamagePercent / 100;
595 AttackedPlayer->CurrentHealth -= ChipDamage;
596 AttackedPlayer->AddMeter(NormalHit.Damage * AttackedPlayer->MeterPercentOnReceiveHitGuard / 100);
597 Player->AddMeter(NormalHit.Damage * Player->MeterPercentOnHitGuard / 100);
598 }
599 if (AttackedPlayer->SuperArmorData.ArmorDamagePercent)
600 {
601 const int32 ArmorDamage = NormalHit.Damage * AttackedPlayer->SuperArmorData.ArmorDamagePercent / 100;
602 AttackedPlayer->CurrentHealth -= ArmorDamage;
603 AttackedPlayer->AddMeter(
604 NormalHit.Damage * AttackedPlayer->MeterPercentOnReceiveHit * AttackedPlayer->
605 SuperArmorData.ArmorDamagePercent / 10000);
606 Player->AddMeter(
607 NormalHit.Damage * Player->MeterPercentOnHit * AttackedPlayer->
608 SuperArmorData.ArmorDamagePercent / 10000);
609 }
610 else
611 {
612 CreateCommonParticle(Particle_Guard, POS_Enemy,
613 FVector(0, 100, 0),
614 FRotator(HitCommon.HitAngle, 0, 0));
615 }
616
617 const FHitData Data = InitHitDataByAttackLevel(false);
618 AttackedPlayer->ReceivedHitCommon = HitCommon;
619 AttackedPlayer->ReceivedHit = Data;
620
621 if (AttackedPlayer->CurrentHealth <= 0)
622 {
623 EHitAction HACT;
624
625 if (AttackedPlayer->PosY == AttackedPlayer->GroundHeight && !(AttackedPlayer->PlayerFlags & PLF_IsKnockedDown))
626 HACT = NormalHit.GroundHitAction;
627 else
628 HACT = NormalHit.AirHitAction;
629
630 AttackedPlayer->HandleHitAction(HACT);
631 }
632 else
633 {
634 Hitstop = Data.Hitstop;
635 AttackedPlayer->Hitstop = Data.Hitstop;
636 }
637 }
638 break;
639 case ARM_Dodge:
640 default:
641 break;
642 }
643 }
644 else if ((AttackedPlayer->AttackFlags & ATK_IsAttacking) == 0)
645 {
646 TriggerEvent(EVT_Hit);
647 if (AttackedPlayer->IsMainPlayer())
648 {
649 TriggerEvent(EVT_HitMainPlayer);
650 }
651
652 if (IsPlayer && Player->PlayerFlags & PLF_HitgrabActive)
653 {
654 AttackedPlayer->JumpToState(State_Universal_ThrowLock);
655 AttackedPlayer->PlayerFlags |= PLF_IsThrowLock;
656 AttackedPlayer->AttackOwner = Player;
657 Player->ThrowExe();
658 return;
659 }
660
661 const FHitData Data = InitHitDataByAttackLevel(false);
662 CreateCommonParticle(HitCommon.HitVFX, POS_Hit,
663 FVector(0, 100, 0),
664 FRotator(HitCommon.HitAngle, 0, 0));
665 PlayCommonSound(HitCommon.HitSFX);
666 AttackedPlayer->ReceivedHitCommon = HitCommon;
667 AttackedPlayer->ReceivedHit = Data;
668 EHitAction HACT;
669
670 if (AttackedPlayer->PosY == AttackedPlayer->GroundHeight && !(AttackedPlayer->PlayerFlags & PLF_IsKnockedDown))
671 HACT = NormalHit.GroundHitAction;
672 else
673 HACT = NormalHit.AirHitAction;
674
675 AttackedPlayer->HandleHitAction(HACT);
676 }
677 else
678 {
679 TriggerEvent(EVT_Hit);
680 TriggerEvent(EVT_CounterHit);
681 if (AttackedPlayer->IsMainPlayer())
682 {
683 TriggerEvent(EVT_HitMainPlayer);
684 TriggerEvent(EVT_CounterHitMainPlayer);
685 }
686
687 AttackedPlayer->AddColor = FLinearColor(5,0.2,0.2,1);
688 AttackedPlayer->MulColor = FLinearColor(1,0.1,0.1,1);
689 AttackedPlayer->AddFadeSpeed = 0.1;
690 AttackedPlayer->MulFadeSpeed = 0.1;
691
692 if (IsPlayer && Player->PlayerFlags & PLF_HitgrabActive)
693 {
694 AttackedPlayer->JumpToState(State_Universal_ThrowLock);
695 AttackedPlayer->PlayerFlags |= PLF_IsThrowLock;
696 AttackedPlayer->AttackOwner = Player;
697 Player->ThrowExe();
698 return;
699 }
700
701 const FHitData CounterData = InitHitDataByAttackLevel(true);
702 CreateCommonParticle(HitCommon.HitVFX, POS_Hit, FVector(0, 100, 0), FRotator(HitCommon.HitAngle, 0, 0));
703 PlayCommonSound(HitCommon.HitSFX);
704 AttackedPlayer->ReceivedHitCommon = HitCommon;
705 AttackedPlayer->ReceivedHit = CounterData;
706 AttackedPlayer->ReceivedHit = CounterData;
707 EHitAction HACT;
708
709 if (AttackedPlayer->PosY == AttackedPlayer->GroundHeight && !(AttackedPlayer->PlayerFlags & PLF_IsKnockedDown))
710 HACT = CounterHit.GroundHitAction;
711 else

1204
1205void ABattleObject::HandleClashCollision(ABattleObject* OtherObj)
1206{
1207 if (AttackFlags & ATK_IsAttacking && AttackFlags & ATK_HitActive && OtherObj->Player->PlayerIndex != Player->PlayerIndex
1208 && OtherObj->AttackFlags & ATK_IsAttacking && OtherObj->AttackFlags & ATK_HitActive)
1209 {
1210 for (int i = 0; i < CollisionArraySize; i++)
1211 {
1212 if (Boxes[i].Type == BOX_Hit)
1213 {
1214 for (int j = 0; j < CollisionArraySize; j++)
1215 {
1216 if (OtherObj->Boxes[j].Type == BOX_Hit)
1217 {
1218 FCollisionBox Hitbox = Boxes[i];
1219
1220 FCollisionBox OtherHitbox = OtherObj->Boxes[j];
1221
1222 if (Direction == DIR_Right)
1223 {
1224 Hitbox.PosX += PosX;
1225 }
1226 else
1227 {
1228 Hitbox.PosX = -Hitbox.PosX + PosX;
1229 }
1230 Hitbox.PosY += PosY;
1231 if (OtherObj->Direction == DIR_Right)
1232 {
1233 OtherHitbox.PosX += OtherObj->PosX;
1234 }
1235 else
1236 {
1237 OtherHitbox.PosX = -OtherHitbox.PosX + OtherObj->PosX;
1238 }
1239 OtherHitbox.PosY += OtherObj->PosY;
1240
1241 if (Hitbox.PosY + Hitbox.SizeY / 2 >= OtherHitbox.PosY - OtherHitbox.SizeY / 2
1242 && Hitbox.PosY - Hitbox.SizeY / 2 <= OtherHitbox.PosY + OtherHitbox.SizeY / 2
1243 && Hitbox.PosX + Hitbox.SizeX / 2 >= OtherHitbox.PosX - OtherHitbox.SizeX / 2
1244 && Hitbox.PosX - Hitbox.SizeX / 2 <= OtherHitbox.PosX + OtherHitbox.SizeX / 2)
1245 {
1246 int CollisionDepthX;
1247 if (Hitbox.PosX < OtherHitbox.PosX)
1248 {
1249 CollisionDepthX = OtherHitbox.PosX - OtherHitbox.SizeX / 2 - (Hitbox.PosX + Hitbox.SizeX / 2);
1250 HitPosX = Hitbox.PosX - CollisionDepthX;
1251 }
1252 else
1253 {
1254 CollisionDepthX = Hitbox.PosX - Hitbox.SizeX / 2 - (OtherHitbox.PosX + OtherHitbox.SizeX / 2);
1255 HitPosX = Hitbox.PosX + CollisionDepthX;
1256 }
1257 int CollisionDepthY;
1258 if (Hitbox.PosY < OtherHitbox.PosY)
1259 {
1260 CollisionDepthY = OtherHitbox.PosY - OtherHitbox.SizeY / 2 - (Hitbox.PosY + Hitbox.SizeY / 2);
1261 HitPosY = Hitbox.PosY - CollisionDepthY;
1262 }
1263 else
1264 {
1265 CollisionDepthY = Hitbox.PosY - Hitbox.SizeY / 2 - (OtherHitbox.PosY + OtherHitbox.SizeY / 2);
1266 HitPosY = Hitbox.PosY + CollisionDepthY;
1267 }
1268
1269 if (IsPlayer && OtherObj->IsPlayer)
1270 {
1271 Hitstop = 16;
1272 OtherObj->Hitstop = 16;
1273 AttackFlags &= ~ATK_HitActive;
1274 OtherObj->AttackFlags &= ~ATK_HitActive;
1275 OtherObj->HitPosX = HitPosX;
1276 OtherObj->HitPosY = HitPosY;
1277 Player->EnableAttacks();
1278 Player->EnableCancelIntoSelf(true);
1279 Player->EnableState(ENB_ForwardDash);
1280 OtherObj->Player->EnableAttacks();
1281 OtherObj->Player->EnableCancelIntoSelf(true);
1282 OtherObj->Player->EnableState(ENB_ForwardDash);
1283 TriggerEvent(EVT_HitOrBlock);
1284 OtherObj->TriggerEvent(EVT_HitOrBlock);
1285 CreateCommonParticle(Particle_Hit_Clash, POS_Hit, FVector(0, 100, 0));
1286 PlayCommonSound(Sound_Hit_Clash);
1287 return;
1288 }
1289 if (!IsPlayer && !OtherObj->IsPlayer)
1290 {
1291 OtherObj->Hitstop = 16;
1292 Hitstop = 16;
1293 AttackFlags &= ~ATK_HitActive;
1294 OtherObj->AttackFlags &= ~ATK_HitActive;
1295 OtherObj->HitPosX = HitPosX;
1296 OtherObj->HitPosY = HitPosY;
1297 TriggerEvent(EVT_HitOrBlock);
1298 OtherObj->TriggerEvent(EVT_HitOrBlock);
1299 CreateCommonParticle(Particle_Hit_Clash, POS_Hit, FVector(0, 100, 0));
1300 PlayCommonSound(Sound_Hit_Clash);
1301 return;
1302 }
1303 return;
1304 }
1305 }
1306 }
1307 }
1308 }
1309 }

1312void ABattleObject::HandleFlip()
1313{
1314 const EObjDir CurrentDir = Direction;
1315 if (!Player->Enemy) return;
1316 if (PosX < Player->Enemy->PosX)
1317 {
1318 SetFacing(DIR_Right);
1319 }
1320 else if (PosX > Player->Enemy->PosX)
1321 {
1322 SetFacing(DIR_Left);
1323 }
1324 if (CurrentDir != Direction)
1325 {
1326 SpeedX = -SpeedX;
1327 Inertia = -Inertia;
1328 if (IsPlayer)
1329 {
1330 Player->StoredInputBuffer.FlipInputsInBuffer();
1331 if (Player->Stance == ACT_Standing && Player->EnableFlags & ENB_Standing)
1332 Player->JumpToState(State_Universal_StandFlip);
1333 else if (Player->Stance == ACT_Crouching && Player->EnableFlags & ENB_Standing)
1334 Player->JumpToState(State_Universal_CrouchFlip);
1335 else if (Player->Stance == ACT_Jumping && Player->EnableFlags & ENB_Jumping)
1336 Player->JumpToState(State_Universal_JumpFlip);
1337 }
1338 }

1341void ABattleObject::PosTypeToPosition(EPosType Type, int32* OutPosX, int32* OutPosY) const
1342{
1343 switch (Type)
1344 {
1345 case POS_Self:
1346 *OutPosX = PosX;
1347 *OutPosY = PosY;
1348 break;
1349 case POS_Player:
1350 *OutPosX = Player->PosX;
1351 *OutPosY = Player->PosY;
1352 break;
1353 case POS_Center:
1354 *OutPosX = PosX;
1355 if (!IsPlayer)
1356 {
1357 *OutPosY = PosY;
1358 break;
1359 }
1360 {
1361 int32 CenterPosY = PosY;
1362 switch (Player->Stance)
1363 {
1364 case ACT_Standing:
1365 case ACT_Jumping:
1366 default:
1367 CenterPosY += 200000;
1368 break;
1369 case ACT_Crouching:
1370 CenterPosY += 90000;
1371 break;
1372 }
1373 *OutPosY = CenterPosY;
1374 }
1375 break;
1376 case POS_Enemy:
1377 *OutPosX = Player->Enemy->PosX;
1378 *OutPosY = Player->Enemy->PosY;
1379 break;
1380 case POS_Hit:
1381 *OutPosX = HitPosX;
1382 *OutPosY = HitPosY;
1383 break;
1384 default:
1385 break;
1386 }

1389void ABattleObject::TriggerEvent(EEventType EventType)
1390{
1391 if (EventType == EVT_Update) UpdateTime++;
1392 if (const auto SubroutineName = EventHandlers[EventType].SubroutineName; SubroutineName != FGameplayTag::EmptyTag)
1393 {
1394 USubroutine* Subroutine = nullptr;
1395
1396 if (const auto CommonIndex = Player->CommonSubroutineNames.Find(SubroutineName); CommonIndex != INDEX_NONE)
1397 Subroutine = Player->CommonSubroutines[CommonIndex];
1398
1399 else if (const auto Index = Player->SubroutineNames.Find(SubroutineName); Index != INDEX_NONE)
1400 Subroutine = Player->Subroutines[Index];
1401
1402 if (!Subroutine) return;
1403
1404 UFunction* const Func = Subroutine->FindFunction(EventHandlers[EventType].FunctionName);
1405 if (IsValid(Func) && Func->ParmsSize == 0)
1406 {
1407 Subroutine->Parent = this;
1408 Subroutine->ProcessEvent(Func, nullptr);
1409 }
1410 return;
1411 }
1412
1413 UState* State = ObjectState;
1414 if (IsPlayer)
1415 State = Player->StoredStateMachine.CurrentState;
1416 if (!IsValid(State))
1417 return;
1418 UFunction* const Func = State->FindFunction(EventHandlers[EventType].FunctionName);
1419 if (IsValid(Func) && Func->ParmsSize == 0)
1420 {
1421 State->ProcessEvent(Func, nullptr);
1422 }
1423}

1425//for collision viewer
1426
1427template<typename T>
1428constexpr auto min(T a, T b)
1429{
1430 return a < b ? a : b;
1431}
1432
1433template<typename T>
1434constexpr auto max(T a, T b)
1435{
1436 return a > b ? a : b;
1437}
1438static void clip_line_y(
1439 const FVector2D &line_a, const FVector2D &line_b,
1440 float min_x, float max_x,
1441 float *min_y, float *max_y)
1442{
1443 const auto delta = line_b - line_a;
1444
1445 if (abs(delta.X) > FLT_EPSILON) {
1446 const auto slope = delta.Y / delta.X;
1447 const auto intercept = line_a.Y - slope * line_a.X;
1448 *min_y = slope * min_x + intercept;
1449 *max_y = slope * max_x + intercept;
1450 } else {
1451 *min_y = line_a.Y;
1452 *max_y = line_b.Y;
1453 }
1454
1455 if (*min_y > *max_y)
1456 std::swap(*min_y, *max_y);
1457}
1458
1459bool line_box_intersection(
1460 const FVector2D &box_min, const FVector2D &box_max,
1461 const FVector2D &line_a, const FVector2D &line_b,
1462 float *entry_fraction, float *exit_fraction)
1463{
1464 // No intersection if line runs along the edge of the box
1465 if (line_a.X == line_b.X && (line_a.X == box_min.X || line_a.X == box_max.X))
1466 return false;
1467
1468 if (line_a.Y == line_b.Y && (line_a.Y == box_min.Y || line_a.Y == box_max.Y))
1469 return false;
1470
1471 // Clip X values to segment within box_min.X and box_max.X
1472 const auto min_x = max(min(line_a.X, line_b.X), box_min.X);
1473 const auto max_x = min(max(line_a.X, line_b.X), box_max.X);
1474
1475 // Check if the line is in the bounds of the box on the X axis
1476 if (min_x > max_x)
1477 return false;
1478
1479 // Clip Y values to segment within min_x and max_x
1480 float min_y, max_y;
1481 clip_line_y(line_a, line_b, min_x, max_x, &min_y, &max_y);
1482
1483 // Clip Y values to segment within box_min.Y and box_max.Y
1484 min_y = max(min_y, (float)box_min.Y);
1485 max_y = min(max_y, (float)box_max.Y);
1486
1487 // Check if the clipped line is in the bounds of the box on the Y axis
1488 if (min_y > max_y)
1489 return false;
1490
1491 const FVector2D entry(
1492 line_a.X < line_b.X ? min_x : max_x,
1493 line_a.Y < line_b.Y ? min_y : max_y);
1494
1495 const FVector2D exit(
1496 line_a.X > line_b.X ? min_x : max_x,
1497 line_a.Y > line_b.Y ? min_y : max_y);
1498
1499 const auto length = (line_b - line_a).Size();
1500 *entry_fraction = (entry - line_a).Size() / length;
1501 *exit_fraction = (exit - line_a).Size() / length;
1502
1503 return true;
1504}

1506void ABattleObject::CollisionView()
1507{
1508 TArray<TArray<FVector2D>> Corners;
1509 TArray<TArray<TArray<FVector2D>>> Lines;
1510 for (auto Box : Boxes)
1511 {
1512 TArray<FVector2D> CurrentCorners;
1513 if (Direction == DIR_Right)
1514 {
1515 CurrentCorners.Add(FVector2D(float(Box.PosX + PosX) / COORD_SCALE - float(Box.SizeX) / COORD_SCALE / 2,
1516 float(Box.PosY + PosY) / COORD_SCALE - float(Box.SizeY) / COORD_SCALE / 2));
1517 CurrentCorners.Add(FVector2D(float(Box.PosX + PosX) / COORD_SCALE + float(Box.SizeX) / COORD_SCALE / 2,
1518 float(Box.PosY + PosY) / COORD_SCALE - float(Box.SizeY) / COORD_SCALE / 2));
1519 CurrentCorners.Add(FVector2D(float(Box.PosX + PosX) / COORD_SCALE + float(Box.SizeX) / COORD_SCALE / 2,
1520 float(Box.PosY + PosY) / COORD_SCALE + float(Box.SizeY) / COORD_SCALE / 2));
1521 CurrentCorners.Add(FVector2D(float(Box.PosX + PosX) / COORD_SCALE - float(Box.SizeX) / COORD_SCALE / 2,
1522 float(Box.PosY + PosY) / COORD_SCALE + float(Box.SizeY) / COORD_SCALE / 2));
1523 }
1524 else
1525 {
1526 CurrentCorners.Add(FVector2D(float(-Box.PosX + PosX) / COORD_SCALE - float(Box.SizeX) / COORD_SCALE / 2,
1527 float(Box.PosY + PosY) / COORD_SCALE - float(Box.SizeY) / COORD_SCALE / 2));
1528 CurrentCorners.Add(FVector2D(float(-Box.PosX + PosX) / COORD_SCALE + float(Box.SizeX) / COORD_SCALE / 2,
1529 float(Box.PosY + PosY) / COORD_SCALE - float(Box.SizeY) / COORD_SCALE / 2));
1530 CurrentCorners.Add(FVector2D(float(-Box.PosX + PosX) / COORD_SCALE + float(Box.SizeX) / COORD_SCALE / 2,
1531 float(Box.PosY + PosY) / COORD_SCALE + float(Box.SizeY) / COORD_SCALE / 2));
1532 CurrentCorners.Add(FVector2D(float(-Box.PosX + PosX) / COORD_SCALE - float(Box.SizeX) / COORD_SCALE / 2,
1533 float(Box.PosY + PosY) / COORD_SCALE + float(Box.SizeY) / COORD_SCALE / 2));
1534 }
1535 Corners.Add(CurrentCorners);
1536 TArray<TArray<FVector2D>> CurrentLines;
1537 for (int j = 0; j < 4; j++)
1538 {
1539 CurrentLines.Add(TArray { CurrentCorners[j] , CurrentCorners[(j + 1) % 4] } );
1540 }
1541 Lines.Add(CurrentLines);
1542 FLinearColor color;
1543 if (Box.Type == BOX_Hit)
1544 color = FLinearColor(1.f, 0.f, 0.f, .25f);
1545 else if (AttackFlags & ATK_IsAttacking)
1546 color = FLinearColor(0.f, 1.f, 1.f, .25f);
1547 else
1548 color = FLinearColor(0.f, 1.f, 0.f, .25f);
1549 for (const auto& LineSet : Lines.Last())
1550 {
1551 auto start = LineSet[0];
1552 auto end = LineSet[1];
1553 DrawDebugLine(GetWorld(), FVector(start.X, 0, start.Y), FVector(end.X, 0, end.Y), color.ToFColor(false), false, 1 / 60, 255, 2.f);
1554 }
1555 }
1556 TArray<FVector2D> CurrentCorners;
1557 CurrentCorners.Add(FVector2D(L / COORD_SCALE, B / COORD_SCALE));
1558 CurrentCorners.Add(FVector2D(R / COORD_SCALE, B / COORD_SCALE));
1559 CurrentCorners.Add(FVector2D(R / COORD_SCALE, T / COORD_SCALE));
1560 CurrentCorners.Add(FVector2D(L / COORD_SCALE, T / COORD_SCALE));
1561 TArray<TArray<FVector2D>> CurrentLines;
1562 for (int j = 0; j < 4; j++)
1563 {
1564 CurrentLines.Add(TArray { CurrentCorners[j] , CurrentCorners[(j + 1) % 4] } );
1565 }
1566 FLinearColor color = FLinearColor(1.f, 1.f, 0.f, .2f);
1567
1568 for (const auto& LineSet : CurrentLines)
1569 {
1570 auto start = LineSet[0];
1571 auto end = LineSet[1];
1572 DrawDebugLine(GetWorld(), FVector(start.X, 0, start.Y), FVector(end.X, 0, end.Y), color.ToFColor(false), false,1 / 60, 255, 2.f);
1573 }
1574}

1628void ABattleObject::UpdateVisuals()
1629{
1630 if (IsPlayer)
1631 {
1632 if (Player->PlayerFlags & PLF_IsOnScreen) SetActorHiddenInGame(false);
1633 else SetActorHiddenInGame(true);
1634 }
1635 FRotator FlipRotation = FRotator::ZeroRotator;
1636 if (Direction == DIR_Left)
1637 {
1638 if (Player->bMirrorWhenFlip && IsPlayer)
1639 {
1640 FlipRotation = FRotator(0, 180, 0);
1641 SetActorScale3D(FVector(1, 1, 1) * ObjectScale);
1642 if (!GameState) SetActorRotation(FlipRotation);
1643 }
1644 else
1645 SetActorScale3D(FVector(-1, 1, 1) * ObjectScale);
1646 }
1647 else
1648 {
1649 SetActorScale3D(FVector(1, 1, 1) * ObjectScale);
1650 }
1651 if (IsValid(GameState))
1652 {
1653 if (SocketName == NAME_None) //only set visual location if not attached to socket
1654 {
1655 SetActorRotation(GameState->BattleSceneTransform.GetRotation() * (ObjectRotation.Quaternion() * FlipRotation.Quaternion()));
1656 FVector Location = FVector(static_cast<float>(PosX) / COORD_SCALE, static_cast<float>(PosZ) / COORD_SCALE, static_cast<float>(PosY) / COORD_SCALE) + ObjectOffset;
1657 Location = GameState->BattleSceneTransform.GetRotation().RotateVector(Location) + GameState->BattleSceneTransform.GetLocation();
1658 SetActorLocation(Location);
1659 }
1660 else
1661 {
1662 FVector FinalSocketOffset = SocketOffset;
1663 if (Direction != DIR_Right)
1664 FinalSocketOffset.Y = -SocketOffset.Y;
1665 const auto Obj = GetBattleObject(SocketObj);
1666 TArray<USkeletalMeshComponent*> SkeletalMeshComponents;
1667 Obj->GetComponents(USkeletalMeshComponent::StaticClass(), SkeletalMeshComponents);
1668 for (const auto Component : SkeletalMeshComponents)
1669 {
1670 if (!Component->DoesSocketExist(SocketName)) continue;
1671 FVector SocketLocation;
1672 FRotator SocketRotation;
1673 Component->GetSocketWorldLocationAndRotation(SocketName, SocketLocation, SocketRotation);
1674 SetActorLocation(FinalSocketOffset + SocketLocation);
1675 SetActorRotation(SocketRotation);
1676 }
1677 }
1678 if (GameState->BattleState.CurrentSequenceTime >= 0)
1679 {
1680 ScreenSpaceDepthOffset = 0;
1681 OrthoBlendActive = FMath::Lerp(OrthoBlendActive, 0, 0.2);
1682 }
1683 else
1684 {
1685 if (IsPlayer)
1686 ScreenSpaceDepthOffset = (MaxPlayerObjects - DrawPriority) * 25;
1687 else
1688 ScreenSpaceDepthOffset = (MaxBattleObjects - DrawPriority) * 15;
1689 OrthoBlendActive = FMath::Lerp(OrthoBlendActive, 1, 0.2);
1690 }
1691 }
1692 else
1693 {
1694 ScreenSpaceDepthOffset = 0;
1695 OrthoBlendActive = 1;
1696 }
1697
1698 if (LinkedActor)
1699 {
1700 LinkedActor->SetActorScale3D(GetActorScale3D());
1701 LinkedActor->SetActorRotation(GetActorRotation());
1702 LinkedActor->SetActorLocation(GetActorLocation());
1703 }
1704
1705 AddColor = FMath::Lerp(AddColor, AddFadeColor, AddFadeSpeed);
1706 MulColor = FMath::Lerp(MulColor, MulFadeColor, MulFadeSpeed);
1707
1708 TInlineComponentArray<UPrimitiveComponent*> Components(this);
1709 GetComponents(Components);
1710 for (const auto Component : Components)
1711 {
1712 for (int64 i = 0; i < Component->GetNumMaterials(); i++)
1713 {
1714 if (const auto MIDynamic = Cast<UMaterialInstanceDynamic>(Component->GetMaterial(i)); IsValid(MIDynamic))
1715 {
1716 MIDynamic->SetScalarParameterValue(FName(TEXT("ScreenSpaceDepthOffset")), ScreenSpaceDepthOffset);
1717 MIDynamic->SetScalarParameterValue(FName(TEXT("OrthoBlendActive")), OrthoBlendActive);
1718 MIDynamic->SetVectorParameterValue(FName(TEXT("AddColor")), AddColor);
1719 MIDynamic->SetVectorParameterValue(FName(TEXT("MulColor")), MulColor);
1720 }
1721 }
1722 if (const auto Mesh = Cast<USkeletalMeshComponent>(Component); IsValid(Mesh))
1723 {
1724 if (const auto MIDynamic = Cast<UMaterialInstanceDynamic>(Mesh->OverlayMaterial); IsValid(MIDynamic))
1725 {
1726 MIDynamic->SetScalarParameterValue(FName(TEXT("ScreenSpaceDepthOffset")), ScreenSpaceDepthOffset);
1727 MIDynamic->SetScalarParameterValue(FName(TEXT("OrthoBlendActive")), OrthoBlendActive);
1728 MIDynamic->SetVectorParameterValue(FName(TEXT("AddColor")), AddColor);
1729 MIDynamic->SetVectorParameterValue(FName(TEXT("MulColor")), MulColor);
1730 }
1731 }
1732 }
1733 FrameBlendPosition = static_cast<float>(MaxCelTime - TimeUntilNextCel) / static_cast<float>(MaxCelTime);
1734 MarkComponentsRenderStateDirty();
1735}

1828 Boxes[j].Type = BOX_Hurt;
1829 Boxes[j].PosX = -10000000;
1830 Boxes[j].PosY = -10000000;
1831 Boxes[j].SizeX = 0;
1832 Boxes[j].SizeY = 0;
1833 }
1834 }
1835 }
1836 if (Player->CollisionData->CollisionFrames[i].CelName == BlendCelName)
1837 {
1838 BlendAnimFrame = Player->CollisionData->CollisionFrames[i].AnimFrame;
1839 for (int j = 0; j < CollisionArraySize; j++)
1840 {
1841 if (j < Player->CollisionData->CollisionFrames[i].Boxes.Num())
1842 {
1843 if (Player->CollisionData->CollisionFrames[i].Boxes[j].Type != BOX_Offset) continue;
1844
1845 NextOffsetX = Player->CollisionData->CollisionFrames[i].Boxes[j].PosX;
1846 NextOffsetY = Player->CollisionData->CollisionFrames[i].Boxes[j].PosY;
1847 }
1848 }
1849 }
1850 }
1851 }

1877
1878void ABattleObject::Update()
1879{
1880 CalculatePushbox();
1881
1882 if (!IsPlayer && StopLinkObj)
1883 {
1884 Hitstop = StopLinkObj->Hitstop;
1885 }
1886
1887 if (Hitstop > 0) //break if hitstop active.
1888 {
1889 Hitstop--;
1890 return;
1891 }
1892
1893 if (!IsPlayer && MiscFlags & MISC_DeactivateOnNextUpdate)
1894 {
1895 ResetObject();
1896 return;
1897 }
1898
1899 if (IsPlayer)
1900 if (Player->PlayerFlags & PLF_IsThrowLock)
1901 return;
1902
1903 if (Timer0 > 0)
1904 {
1905 --Timer0;
1906 if (Timer0 == 0) TriggerEvent(EVT_Timer0);
1907 }
1908 if (Timer1 > 0)
1909 {
1910 --Timer1;
1911 if (Timer1 == 0) TriggerEvent(EVT_Timer1);
1912 }
1913
1914 if (MiscFlags & MISC_FlipEnable)
1915 HandleFlip();
1916
1917 Move();
1918
1919 GameState->SetScreenBounds();
1920 GameState->SetStageBounds();
1921
1922 if (PosY == GroundHeight && PrevPosY != GroundHeight)
1923 {
1924 if (!IsPlayer)
1925 TriggerEvent(EVT_Landing);
1926 SpeedX = 0;
1927 }
1928
1929 if (!IsPlayer)
1930 {
1931 if (ActionTime == 0)
1932 {
1933 ObjectState->Init();
1934 }
1935
1936 ObjectState->CallExec();
1937 TriggerEvent(EVT_Update);
1938 TimeUntilNextCel--;
1939 if (TimeUntilNextCel == 0)
1940 CelIndex++;
1941
1942 GameState->SetScreenBounds();
1943 GameState->SetStageBounds();
1944 ActionTime++;
1945
1946 if (MiscFlags & MISC_DeactivateIfBeyondBounds)
1947 {
1948 if (PosX > GameState->BattleState.ScreenBounds + 360000 + GameState->BattleState.StageBounds
1949 || PosX < -GameState->BattleState.ScreenBounds - 360000 - GameState->BattleState.StageBounds)
1950 DeactivateObject();
1951 }
1952 }
1953}

2266int32 ABattleObject::CalculateDistanceBetweenPoints(EDistanceType Type, EObjType Obj1, EPosType Pos1, EObjType Obj2,
2267 EPosType Pos2)
2268{
2269 const ABattleObject* Actor1 = GetBattleObject(Obj1);
2270 const ABattleObject* Actor2 = GetBattleObject(Obj2);
2271 if (IsValid(Actor1) && IsValid(Actor2))
2272 {
2273 int32 PosX1 = 0;
2274 int32 PosX2 = 0;
2275 int32 PosY1 = 0;
2276 int32 PosY2 = 0;
2277
2278 Actor1->PosTypeToPosition(Pos1, &PosX1, &PosY1);
2279 Actor2->PosTypeToPosition(Pos2, &PosX2, &PosY2);
2280
2281 int32 ObjDist;
2282
2283 switch (Type)
2284 {
2285 case DIST_Distance:
2286 ObjDist = isqrt(static_cast<int64>(PosX2 - PosX1) * static_cast<int64>(PosX2 - PosX1) + static_cast<int64>(PosY2 - PosY1) * static_cast<int64>(PosY2 - PosY1));
2287 break;
2288 case DIST_DistanceX:
2289 ObjDist = abs(PosX2 - PosX1);
2290 break;
2291 case DIST_DistanceY:
2292 ObjDist = abs(PosY2 - PosY1);
2293 break;
2294 case DIST_FrontDistanceX:
2295 {
2296 int DirFlag = 1;
2297 if (Actor1->Direction == DIR_Left)
2298 {
2299 DirFlag = -1;
2300 }
2301 ObjDist = (PosX2 - PosX1) * DirFlag;
2302 }
2303 break;
2304 default:
2305 return 0;
2306 }
2307 return ObjDist;
2308 }
2309 return 0;
2310}

2313{
2314 const ABattleObject* Actor1 = GetBattleObject(Obj1);
2315 const ABattleObject* Actor2 = GetBattleObject(Obj2);
2316 if (IsValid(Actor1) && IsValid(Actor2))

2318 int32 PosX1 = 0;

2320 int32 PosY1 = 0;
2321 int32 PosY2 = 0;
2322
2323 Actor1->PosTypeToPosition(Pos1, &PosX1, &PosY1);
2324 Actor2->PosTypeToPosition(Pos2, &PosX2, &PosY2);
2325
2326 const auto X = abs(PosX2 - PosX1);
2327 const auto Y = PosY2 - PosY1;
2328
2329 return UNightSkyBlueprintFunctionLibrary::Vec2Angle_x1000(X, Y);
2330 }
